---
title: Double Beef Rump Steak & Braised Leek Take your cooking skills to the next level!
description: Time to unleash your inner chef! Tonight we’re digging in to meltingly tender beef rump with leeks, braised to bring out all their natural sweetness. We think the real star of the show here is the twice-cooked roast potatoes - don’t worry, we’ve given you all the tips and tricks to achieve your crispiest roasties yet!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
